      <p class="- topic/p ">The standards and directives that the Reality in this manual conforms
with.</p>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">International Standards</title>
         <p class="- topic/p ">The Reality mentioned
in this manual is designed according to the international standards
listed in the table.</p>
